user_question: Determine the pKa of the amine group in semaglutide's structure

3) Run a microscopic pKa workflow targeting nitrogen sites (N) to obtain site-specific pKa values. We’ll identify the pKa for the primary amine(s). If multiple amines exist (e.g., N-terminus and Lys side chain), I’ll report both, highlighting the N-terminal amine unless you specify otherwise.
4) Smart polling of the workflow until completion.
5) Retrieve results and extract the amine pKa(s).
